1. qmake -config [debug|release]
2. make
3. sudo make install
4. CONFIG += libircclient-qt
5. enjoy!

NOTE: ICU support is enabled by default. If you do not have ICU installed or
      if you want to disable the ICU support for other reasons, you must 
      comment out the following line from icu.pri:
      
      # DEFINES += HAVE_ICU
